videos.description: Herb Jones intercepts a UCF pass and throws it down for the easy 2 points in the first half for the Crimson Tide.
videos.headline: Alabama's Jones steals and throws it down

videos.description: Donta Hall gets the dish from Dazon Ingram and finishes with authority in the second half.
videos.headline: Bama's Hall slams it home

videos.description: Terrell Allen feeds a wide open Chad Brown for the flush in the second half.
videos.headline: UCF's Allen drops a dime

videos.description: Rokas Ulvydas is wide open and misses a dunk in the second half for the Knights.
videos.headline: UCF's Ulvydas misses easy dunk

videos.description: Collin Sexton hits a defender with a behind the back pass and then hits teammate john Petty with a no look pass in the second half.
videos.headline: Alabama's Sexton puts on a show

videos.description: Dino Gaudio and Dave Neal speak with UCF head coach Johnny Dawkins about his team's 65-62 victory.
videos.headline: UCF outlasts Alabama
